To church.

40:46.433 --> 40:47.666
What?

40:47.668 --> 40:49.735
When I was in his camp,

40:49.737 --> 40:53.472
he always stopped by St. Theodore's
when he was in New York.

40:53.474 --> 40:55.907
The church is on Broadway and 24th,

40:55.909 --> 40:58.577
which is five minutes away
from his 4:30 meeting.

40:58.579 --> 41:01.079
